item.description: Functional Form This theme has a form-to-email feature built in, thanks to the simple Formspree integration. All you need to activate the form is a valid recipient email address saved in the front matter of the form (/content/forms/contact.md). Of course, the example shown below (your@email.here) must not be used. Please use your actual email address. # please replace with a valid Formspree form id or email address formspree_form_id: your@email.here Update that file and you’re ready to begin receiving submissions.
